statements: SELECT * FROM property_sales_data
SELECT property_id, property_address, sale_price, sale_date FROM property_sales_data WHERE market_demand_level = 'high'
SELECT property_id, property_address FROM property_sales_data WHERE sale_price > 500000
SELECT property_address, sale_price FROM property_sales_data ORDER BY sale_date DESC
SELECT property_id, property_address, market_demand_level FROM property_sales_data WHERE sale_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-06-30'
SELECT * FROM property_sales_data WHERE sale_price > 500000 ORDER BY sale_date DESC
SELECT property_id, property_address FROM property_sales_data WHERE market_demand_level = 'high'
SELECT property_address, sale_price, sale_date FROM property_sales_data WHERE sale_price BETWEEN 100000 AND 300000 ORDER BY sale_price ASC
SELECT * FROM property_sales_data WHERE sale_date >= '2022-01-01' AND market_demand_level = 'low' ORDER BY property_id
SELECT property_id, property_address, sale_price FROM property_sales_data WHERE sale_price = (SELECT MAX(sale_price) FROM property_sales_data)
SELECT * FROM property_sales WHERE property_type = 'House' ORDER BY sale_price DESC;
SELECT property_id, property_type, sale_price FROM property_sales WHERE sale_date = '2022-01-01';
SELECT property_type, COUNT(*) AS total_sales FROM property_sales GROUP BY property_type;
SELECT * FROM market_demand WHERE demand_level > 5 ORDER BY demand_level ASC;
SELECT demand_id, property_type, market_trend FROM market_demand WHERE market_trend LIKE '%high%' ORDER BY demand_id DESC;
SELECT property_id, property_type, sale_price FROM property_sales WHERE sale_price > 10000 ORDER BY sale_date DESC LIMIT 5
SELECT * FROM property_sales WHERE sale_price BETWEEN 50000 AND 100000 ORDER BY sale_date ASC LIMIT 10
SELECT property_type, COUNT(*) as total_sales, AVG(sale_price) as avg_price FROM property_sales GROUP BY property_type ORDER BY total_sales DESC

SELECT p.property_id, p.property_type, m.demand_level FROM property_sales p INNER JOIN market_demand m ON p.property_type = m.property_type WHERE m.market_trend = 'High Demand' ORDER BY m.demand_level DESC LIMIT 5
SELECT property_id, property_type, sale_price FROM property_sales WHERE property_type ='Apartment' ORDER BY sale_price DESC LIMIT 5
SELECT * FROM property_prices ORDER BY price DESC;
SELECT property_id, property_type, price FROM property_prices WHERE property_type = 'House';
SELECT sale_id, buyer_name, sale_price FROM sales_history WHERE sale_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT property_id, property_location, price FROM property_prices WHERE property_type = 'Apartment' AND property_location = 'New York';
SELECT property_type, COUNT(*) AS total_records FROM property_prices GROUP BY property_type;
SELECT property_id, property_type, price FROM property_prices WHERE property_location = 'New York' ORDER BY price DESC;
SELECT property_id, property_location, price FROM property_prices WHERE price > 100000 ORDER BY property_location ASC;
SELECT property_type, total_demands, demand_date FROM market_demand WHERE total_demands > 50 ORDER BY demand_date DESC;
SELECT sale_id, sale_price, buyer_name FROM sales_history WHERE seller_name = 'John Doe' ORDER BY sale_price ASC;
SELECT * FROM property_prices JOIN sales_history ON property_prices.property_id = sales_history.property_id WHERE sale_price > 500000 ORDER BY property_prices.price DESC;
SELECT * FROM property_sales ORDER BY sale_date DESC;
SELECT property_name, property_address, property_size FROM property_details WHERE property_size >= 100;
SELECT property_id, sale_price, sale_date FROM property_sales WHERE sale_price > 500000 ORDER BY sale_price ASC;
SELECT property_type, demand_level FROM market_demand WHERE property_type = 'House';
SELECT trend_date, trend_type, trend_description FROM property_trends ORDER BY trend_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM property_sales ORDER BY sale_date DESC, sale_price ASC LIMIT 10
SELECT property_id, property_name, property_address FROM property_details WHERE property_age > 10
SELECT property_id, property_name, property_address, property_size FROM property_details WHERE property_size BETWEEN 500 AND 1000
SELECT property_id, trend_date, trend_description FROM property_trends WHERE trend_type = 'Market Analysis'
SELECT property_id, sale_date, sale_price FROM property_sales WHERE property_id IN (SELECT property_id FROM property_details WHERE property_age > 5)
SELECT * FROM property_listings;
SELECT property_id, property_type, listing_price FROM property_listings WHERE listing_date = '2022-01-01';
SELECT property_id, property_type, listing_price FROM property_listings ORDER BY listing_price DESC;
SELECT property_id, property_type, listing_price FROM property_listings WHERE property_type = 'Apartment';
SELECT property_id, property_type, listing_price FROM property_listings WHERE listing_price > 100000 ORDER BY listing_price ASC;
SELECT * FROM property_listings WHERE listing_price > 100000 ORDER BY listing_date DESC;
SELECT property_type, listing_price FROM property_listings WHERE listing_price BETWEEN 50000 AND 80000 ORDER BY property_type ASC;
SELECT sale_id, property_id, sale_price, sale_date, buyer_name FROM sales_data WHERE sale_price < 50000 ORDER BY sale_date DESC;
SELECT trend_description FROM market_trends WHERE trend_date >= '2022-01-01' ORDER BY trend_date ASC;
SELECT * FROM buyer_feedback WHERE rating >= 4 ORDER BY feedback_date DESC;
